on october 31 , 2000 at 11 : 18 pm , singapore airlines ' sq-006 attempted to take off from chiang kai shek international airport for los angeles . in the course of the take off , the plane entered 05-right runway . the plane then hit two dredgers that were on the runway . the impact caused an explosion and the death of 83 passengers . more than 100 passengers were injured in the accident .
