from the date of the crash till now , taoyuan district court chief prosecutor wang teng-sheng in charge of the case was promoted chief prosecutor for taichung . chen sou-huang filled his position . the case was then taken over by prosecutor huang mo-hsin but he was also transferred to taipei later . the case is currently the responsibility of chiang yuan-chen .
sac originally says that they can complete the investigation by the end of last year . sac subsequently delayed the report to end of january . by january , sac changed the report date to end of february and there is no further news since then . after pressed by the prosecutor 's office , sac has now undertaken to delver a report by the end of april .
the destination of sq-006 was los angeles and some passengers are americans . hence , some family members of passengers who died in the crash have already commenced legal actions in u.s. courts for damages against singapore airlines and also in some cases , against taiwan 's civil aeronautics administration .
